{"tid":1900972,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人咪撚黎考DSE!","createTime":"2020-02-27T14:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T05:33:15.000Z","uid":325346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8a5bf385b6ca0a004bc2b6dcbe3055910c3ed84c","tid":1900972,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:17:47.000Z","msg":"由於DSE下月正式開考、大約有700位居住深圳的蝗子蝗女會黎考試。<br />\n<br />\n由於入境有十四天隔離的規例、北區與大埔的校長會希望為支那考生準備隔壁營（Study camp)、並促請政府安排佢地入隔離設施。日校考生大約有三百多人、有部份在港有家人/朋友收留、餘下北區大約有120人與大埔有10人在香港無家要處理佢地。<br />\n<br />\n咁就咪撚黎考、下年先考啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反正考左都升唔到大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有四月開學香港點處理班蝗子蝗女？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留班啦"},{"pid":"410b5d0f758b148addb02f90edc14875919843df","tid":1900972,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:18:43.000Z","msg":"Source :南早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdd7e225603db233edcf995927db8bd4358e2cd","tid":1900972,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:37:13.000Z","msg":"香港多多隔離營都唔夠、四月一大班蝗子蝗女日上日落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1de8c4f5df576dfa919113c12f1f579438abbc","tid":1900972,"uid":222809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"借推po<br />\n太子站CCTV唔見佐，有無巴打搵得返<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fdxyyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fdxyyS</a><br />\nHope to see you all in 229"},{"pid":"1226bdd8a744e5493cd8ba70af4fb69f3768d1ed","tid":1900972,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:52:22.000Z","msg":"班蝗子蝗女今年唔考<br />\n下年一係當日校考生重考（政府俾埋考試費）<br />\n一係當自